Description: LEDStrip
        ========
        
        Python simulation of WS2812 (or probably other WS-type LEDs) LED strips commonly used by NeoPixel API.
        
        
        ## Example 
        ```
        from led import LEDSim
        import cv2
        import numpy as np
        
        pixel = LEDSim()
        pixel.fill((0,0,0))
        
        p = 0
        for r in range(1,6):
        	for g in range(1,6):
        		for b in range(1,6):
        			pixel[p] = (r,g,b)
        			p += 1
        
        pixel.visualize()
        ```
